    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Yogigr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"86d0845b-e259-55cc-a02f-ac8faeb73439","excerpt":"Kenapa kita perlu mematikan keyboard? Ada beberapa alasan kenapa saya harus/perlu mematikan keyboard, diantaranya adalah: Ada salah satu atau lebih tombol diâ€¦","html":"<h4>Kenapa kita perlu mematikan keyboard?</h4>\n<p>Ada beberapa alasan kenapa saya harus/perlu mematikan keyboard, diantaranya adalah:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Ada salah satu atau lebih tombol di keyboard yang error (menekan sendiri). Jika ini terjadi, pekerjaan kita akan terganggu. Salah satu contoh, tombol <strong>Backspace</strong> yang menekan sendiri, jika kita sendang menulis dokumen, pasti tidak akan pernah selesai karena selalu terhapus huruf demi huruf.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Lebih nyaman pakai keyboard external, karena sudah banyak tombol keyboard internal yang mati.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Mungkin ada alasan lain selain yang saya utarakan diatas.</p>\n<h4>Bagaimana cara mematikan / disable keyboard di Ubuntu?</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Sebelum disable, ketahui dulu nomor <strong>id</strong> dan nomor <strong>master</strong> dengan menjalankan perintah:</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">xinput list</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa21eac845e929943cf9ab80e7fa6a0a/7e4a6/xinput-list.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.53164556962025%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"alt xinput list\"\n        title=\"alt xinput list\"\n        src=\"/static/aa21eac845e929943cf9ab80e7fa6a0a/f058b/xinput-list.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa21eac845e929943cf9ab80e7fa6a0a/c26ae/xinput-list.png 158w,\n/static/aa21eac845e929943cf9ab80e7fa6a0a/6bdcf/xinput-list.png 315w,\n/static/aa21eac845e929943cf9ab80e7fa6a0a/f058b/xinput-list.png 630w,\n/static/aa21eac845e929943cf9ab80e7fa6a0a/40601/xinput-list.png 945w,\n/static/aa21eac845e929943cf9ab80e7fa6a0a/7e4a6/xinput-list.png 952w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Dari output diatas kita mendapatkan informasi data nomor <strong>id</strong> dan <strong>master</strong> dari keyboard internal yang akan saya matikan, yaitu <strong>AT Translated Set 2 keyboard id=15\t[slave  keyboard (3)]</strong>, <strong>15</strong> adalah nomor <strong>id</strong> dan <strong>3</strong> adalah nomor master. Informasi itu akan saya butuhkan ketika akan menyalakan kembali keyboard.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Mematikan Keyboard. Jalankan perintah:</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">xinput float <span class=\"token number\">15</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Untuk melihat perubahan, jalankan lagi perintah:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">xinput list</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/70b1320857024daffc66cd4025e2dbfb/ecf19/xinput-float.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.79746835443038%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"alt xinput float\"\n        title=\"alt xinput float\"\n        src=\"/static/70b1320857024daffc66cd4025e2dbfb/f058b/xinput-float.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/70b1320857024daffc66cd4025e2dbfb/c26ae/xinput-float.png 158w,\n/static/70b1320857024daffc66cd4025e2dbfb/6bdcf/xinput-float.png 315w,\n/static/70b1320857024daffc66cd4025e2dbfb/f058b/xinput-float.png 630w,\n/static/70b1320857024daffc66cd4025e2dbfb/40601/xinput-float.png 945w,\n/static/70b1320857024daffc66cd4025e2dbfb/ecf19/xinput-float.png 948w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Sudah terlihat perubahannya bukan? saya test keyboardnya dan berhasil di disable.</p>\n<h4>Bagaimana cara menyalakan kembali Keyboard?</h4>\n<p>Jalankan perintah:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">xinput reattach <span class=\"token number\">15</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>15</strong> adalah <strong>id</strong>, sedangan <strong>3</strong> adalah <strong>master</strong></p>\n<p>Cek kembali perubahan</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">xinput list</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3c96a1d54a066cbbd3fb7fbc410ba58c/d9199/reattach.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.43037974683544%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"alt reattach\"\n        title=\"alt reattach\"\n        src=\"/static/3c96a1d54a066cbbd3fb7fbc410ba58c/f058b/reattach.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3c96a1d54a066cbbd3fb7fbc410ba58c/c26ae/reattach.png 158w,\n/static/3c96a1d54a066cbbd3fb7fbc410ba58c/6bdcf/reattach.png 315w,\n/static/3c96a1d54a066cbbd3fb7fbc410ba58c/f058b/reattach.png 630w,\n/static/3c96a1d54a066cbbd3fb7fbc410ba58c/40601/reattach.png 945w,\n/static/3c96a1d54a066cbbd3fb7fbc410ba58c/d9199/reattach.png 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Dari output diatas, status nya sudah berubah kembali. Saya test keyboardnya dan sudah berhasil enable lagi.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Mematikan Sementara Keyboard Internal Laptop di Ubuntu","date":"September 25, 2021","description":"Cara mematikan sementara keyboard internal laptop di Ubuntu di Terminal."}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/instalasi-laravel-di-ubuntu-server/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Instalasi Laravel di Ubuntu Server"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/akses-repository-github-tanpa-login/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Akses Repository Github tanpa Login"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"86d0845b-e259-55cc-a02f-ac8faeb73439","previousPostId":"0b58537c-d380-54c3-b1d7-7992637940d1","nextPostId":"9f659ded-5295-54e9-a5ac-6a91cd33466e"}},
